33
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,080
Divide the numerator
by 3, you get 1.

34
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:47,570
Divide the denominator
by 3, you get 3.

35
00:01:47,570 --> 00:01:55,800
So this is 22 plus 1/3, which is
